<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service-government-social-research-profession/about/personal-information-charter> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "This privacy notice sets out how the Government Social Research Recruitment Campaign will use your personal data, and your rights under Articles 13 and, or 14 of the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR). The Government Social Research (GSR) is part of HM Treasury, which makes HM Treasury the data controller for personal data processed by GSR."@en .
